column5: Hey guys,  Just wondering if anyone has been out in the last few days. Wondering if all ice is gone?
Never heard of that lake before.
Come on man it's Scugog or better known as Scubog
Ice is gone, today was very choppy and windy.  Most guys said they werent finding the crappie.  We need another warm spell
The last of the ice went out last weekend.
